content.taskInstructions:
Instructions


Review automated scan data for anomalies.

Scan Monster


1. Verify that the Scan Monster data (nmap/Burp) was imported correctly when the scan is complete.
2. Review the Sources tab and sanity check what was imported. Are any obvious scan types missing? Are any obvious websites missing that Burp should have scanned?
3. If any of the expected scan data is missing, raise the concern in the #services or #dev-questions Slack channels to get assistance.

ASM


1. Review the CSV export data for accuracy.
2. Review the Documents tab to ensure the CSV files were uploaded.

Nessus/Nexpose


1. Review the sources tab to verify the Nessus/Nexpose data was imported correctly.
